record.author: J.P.B. de Josselin de Jong
record.notes:
J.P.B. [Jan Petrus Benjamin] de Josselin de Jong. 1987. Wetan fieldnotes: some eastern Indonesian texts. Dordrecht, Holland; Providence, RI, USA: Foris Publications.
These are de Jong's 1933-1934 field notes from his field research in the Babar archipelago.
